what is a cool mom one of my distant friend's moms doesn't care if she stays out late curses has sex or goes to unsupervised parties she is i am i'm due to give birth to my first child a baby boy december st and i'm getting married in a month or so i've been thinking a lot about parenting and my friend calls her mom the coolest mom ever but to me a cool mom is a mom who is jumping for joy during her pregnancy reading up on how to treat an earache songs to sing them to sleep to and picking out baby clothes a mom who gives her child tons of kisses and hugs and never goes a day without telling them she loves them a mom who always knows where her child is and when they'll be back and worries while they're gone a mom who couldn't care less if her child is gay or straight skinny or chubby preppy or punk just as long as they're happy a mom who puts her child before herself and makes sacrificies without a moments hesitation am i wrong you have answered your own question sounds like you are going to make a great mom congratulations ahead of time on your baby Rent (musical) EastEnders Phoebe Buffay's songs Kurt Cobain Friends Humphrey Bogart Shaggy dog story Kyle Broflovski Eric Cartman Laura Schlessinger Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Charmed Pok__mon Live! Social rule Avenue Q Knots Landing Recurring South Park characters The Ashlee Simpson Show Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Yoko Ono Little Britain Abortion debate Child sexuality 2005 trial of Michael Jackson Series finale Melanie Wilkes Frankie Laine The Fairly OddParents Piccolo Junior Saga One Tree Hill (TV series) Care Bears Cartman Joins NAMBLA Childbirth St. Elmo's Fire (film) Ren and Stimpy Miss Saigon Futurama (TV series - season 5) Blood on the Tracks Rocko's Modern Life Le Malade imaginaire Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Everwood The Marshall Mathers LP Fiddler on the Roof Doug Nine Inch Nails Transsexuality Jacob Pop punk Days of our Lives The McGuire Sisters The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy Bab